Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.26,0:00:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优秀的战舰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.63,0:00:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦参与战斗就似乎不得不背负相对的风险
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.60,0:00:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都说抚子是地球联合军中最优秀的战舰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.41,0:00:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以，我们才会战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.42,0:00:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"机动战舰"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.80,0:00:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍着痛苦所踢起的小石头
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.75,0:00:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若反弹回来也会变成钻石
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.49,0:00:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上到手的梦想不算是梦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.20,0:01:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是请坚信它一定会实现
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.87,0:01:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢从不气馁的你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.21,0:01:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有想哭的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.61,0:01:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会永远永远在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.01,0:01:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YOU GET BURNINC
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.61,0:01:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你的方式骄傲地去面对
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.81,0:01:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去热衷的日子是梦的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.71,0:01:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YOU GET BURNINC
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.31,0:01:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将那碎片收集起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.16,0:01:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便能看见以明天为目标的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.25,0:01:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TO BE...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.60,0:01:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GOING YOUR DAY'S GROW UP
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.87,0:01:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站在联合军前头的抚子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.97,0:02:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也被敌军当成杀父仇人般集中攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.48,0:02:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然对方不肯罢休我们也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.95,0:02:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻底地干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.25,0:02:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国家的兴亡就全靠我们的奋斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.32,0:02:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.42,0:02:13.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提起精神提起精神
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.52,0:02:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会轮的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.73,0:02:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.00,0:02:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AESTIVALIS全机都已出动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.60,0:02:27.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"那忘不了的日子"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.60,0:02:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.60,0:02:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，逮到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.21,0:02:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.08,0:02:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.19,0:02:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的混帐蜥蜴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.76,0:02:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.03,0:02:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部攻击都是从抚子来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.60,0:02:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.26,0:02:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岂有此理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.30,0:03:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么，发生什么事了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.11,0:03:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AESTIVALIS队连友军也攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.24,0:03:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击友军?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.34,0:03:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击诱导装置没有异常
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.05,0:03:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抚子的AESTIVALIS全都在攻击敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.45,0:03:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人，敌人是那边吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.72,0:03:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抚子的AESTIVALIS\N正在对敌军与联合军双方进行攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.26,0:03:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么，攻击停止停止
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.46,0:03:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人在极近距离
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.83,0:03:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在停止攻击的话我方会全军覆没
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.70,0:03:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，攻击敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.40,0:03:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要攻击敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.34,0:03:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是打算攻击敌人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.97,0:03:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是怎么会变成这样啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.44,0:03:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，想点办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.11,0:03:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺其自然吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.45,0:03:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在干什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.96,0:03:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抚子本身没有受到攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.96,0:03:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不幸中的大幸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.86,0:04:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之\N各人照顾好自己出动支援的AESTIVALIS
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.80,0:04:03.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没有驾驶员了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.07,0:04:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.47,0:04:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该我出场了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.04,0:04:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辅佐舰长，这是副官的职责
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.81,0:04:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，不光是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.84,0:04:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合香
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.78,0:04:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.75,0:04:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合香
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.32,0:04:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.36,0:04:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯，请回答，纯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.17,0:04:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这天的战斗真是乱七八糟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.61,0:04:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌方也被不分敌我攻击的抚子搞迷糊了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.21,0:04:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草草中止攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.18,0:04:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为不想被卷入抚子不明原因的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.02,0:04:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联合军也撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.12,0:04:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何大家平安无事就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.13,0:05:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AESTIVALIS也几乎只有擦伤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.25,0:05:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂，这个太过份了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.00,0:05:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯，为什么你要上去?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.24,0:05:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么，你想说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.37,0:05:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是手语
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.08,0:05:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说\N在人手不足的抚子上这是身为副官的义务
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.18,0:05:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这虽然很好\N可是要上去时要穿飞行装啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.19,0:05:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说什么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.15,0:05:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一切都是为了百合香，他说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.96,0:05:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是为了百合香穿上飞行装也比较好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.89,0:05:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今，我不想跟你啰唆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.63,0:05:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，别多说了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.24,0:05:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.30,0:05:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶AESTIVALIS的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.34,0:05:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少要系上安全带
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.28,0:05:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好脖子伤得不严重
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.88,0:05:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过暂时无法好好说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.98,0:06:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我暂时不能说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.89,0:06:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我想说的是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.85,0:06:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常都只有对百合香的爱语但却…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.40,0:06:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白痴!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.26,0:06:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯，加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.83,0:06:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要以为没人伤亡就高兴得太早
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:18.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道这战舰一艘多少钱吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.34,0:06:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是我打下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.80,0:06:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.11,0:06:24.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这艘毛地黄比抚子更贵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.08,0:06:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也打下了五十架
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.44,0:06:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就光而言很不错了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.55,0:06:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.91,0:06:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.78,0:06:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细看的话每一架都有联合军的标志
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.55,0:06:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手，住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.35,0:06:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说只是也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.89,0:06:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只说我的击落数
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.73,0:06:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共78架
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.06,0:06:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌我两方加起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.93,0:06:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,62架是我方的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.13,0:06:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.20,0:06:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人你从刚才就都不出声
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.74,0:06:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.50,0:06:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没大家那么惨啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.14,0:06:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来打算攻击敌军的郁金香
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.68,0:07:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是毁的却是联合军的燃料基地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.21,0:07:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你，你知道那基地的建设费吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.25,0:07:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些不是都有保险吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.95,0:07:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.09,0:07:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是至少要花慰问金吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.72,0:07:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何我方无人伤亡真是奇迹般地幸运
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.23,0:07:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慰问金要再增加的话真不知要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.40,0:07:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过有一名脑震荡后遗症的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.14,0:07:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那，最主要的原因是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.27,0:07:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会攻击联合军呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.84,0:07:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们又不是故意去做的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.78,0:07:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们所爱的是绿色的地球
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.18,0:07:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们绝不可能背叛联合军的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.75,0:07:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说是整备不良了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.08,0:07:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这话我可不能当做没听见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.52,0:07:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说我们的安全整备有漏洞是不是?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.99,0:07:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经过连日的战斗多少都会有些失误不是?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.16,0:07:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维修部门的疲劳度也不容忽视啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.80,0:07:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管疲劳不疲劳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.00,0:07:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整备失败是会出人命的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.70,0:07:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整备的好坏关系着生命安全
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.84,0:08:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.70,0:08:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我虽然在女人方面失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.41,0:08:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是机械的整备我绝不会失败
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.81,0:08:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别把你们的疏失都怪到我们头上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.24,0:08:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.15,0:08:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞行员或整备士都没有缺陷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.72,0:08:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那原因是什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.58,0:08:15.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，为了查清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.99,0:08:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联合军的调查团正朝我们这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.09,0:08:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们一直唠叨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.23,0:08:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是我们抚子的防卫攻击电脑出了问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.77,0:08:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以，不要，那不是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.17,0:08:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.04,0:08:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.51,0:08:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道，我什么都没做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.18,0:08:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从调查船逃出的救生艇正在求救
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.42,0:08:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，又有攻击命令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.96,0:08:54.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁下的命令?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.49,0:08:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.49,0:08:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以打，那个不是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.03,0:09:03.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收容地球军的调查船救生艇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.97,0:09:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被抚子误射的调查员们不可能冷静的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.21,0:09:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,片面指责抚子的缺陷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.78,0:09:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之说别人坏话是最轻松的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.09,0:09:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用我说，电脑有学习机能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.09,0:09:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会根据经验进行学习采取最妥善的措施
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.76,0:09:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抚子的电脑它
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.40,0:09:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是"思兼"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.83,0:09:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，是电脑的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.23,0:09:40.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给只不过是道具的电脑取名字
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.27,0:09:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是二十世纪末的恶习
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.41,0:09:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是思兼就是思兼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.77,0:09:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是重钟还是轻钟都无所谓\N(音同思兼)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.48,0:09:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之抚子的电脑中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.38,0:09:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有过去突破防线的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.10,0:09:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说\N它已经把联合军是妨碍抚子行动的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.72,0:09:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这段记忆学起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.09,0:10:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此与地球联合军共同作战会产生抗拒反应
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.76,0:10:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打个比方来说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像是被竞争对手吸收合并
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做牛做马的上班族
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.73,0:10:13.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个比喻真简单易懂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.50,0:10:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉，我了解，我了解啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.01,0:10:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作压力累积过多的话人是会崩溃的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.74,0:10:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电脑的话则会进入冻结状态
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.41,0:10:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是只是冻结的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.88,0:10:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要把变成Bug的资料消掉再重新设定就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.28,0:10:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思兼具有自动重新设定功能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.42,0:10:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这电脑所学的对联合军的敌对意识太深了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.23,0:10:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次重新设定就会增加压力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.59,0:10:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终至演变成像这次的攻击行动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.06,0:10:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解决的方法就是完全消除学习记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.63,0:10:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后改写新的程式
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.20,0:10:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.64,0:10:49.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.17,0:10:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样随随便便可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.08,0:10:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样做的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.41,0:10:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抚子好不容易到火星所学到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.21,0:11:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与敌人战斗的有效率的对应记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.18,0:11:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也会被完全消除
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.65,0:11:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抚子是属于联合军的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.62,0:11:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单独行动时的记忆有百害而无一利
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.53,0:11:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.96,0:11:14.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为保卫地球而战的是人类不是机器
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.66,0:11:18.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用说，抚子是在联合军旗下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.37,0:11:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须忘掉与联合军敌对的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.47,0:11:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘掉就是彻底舍去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.67,0:11:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是大人的藉口而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.88,0:11:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对自己不利的事情只要忘掉就好的藉口
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.98,0:11:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人们都太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.45,0:11:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉璃…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.20,0:11:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…怎么每个人打扮都是一样的?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.30,0:11:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.34,0:11:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"抚子电脑控制室"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.14,0:11:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切换成由副电脑管制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.55,0:11:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,INSTALL开始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.70,0:12:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不消除所有的资料就不行吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.40,0:12:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.70,0:12:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.90,0:12:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改写让思兼绝对服从的程式
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.10,0:12:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抚子从此就脱胎换骨了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.69,0:12:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对呀 从民用船变成真正的战舰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.75,0:12:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只为军方工作的船
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.70,0:12:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.75,0:12:21.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么，百合香
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.38,0:12:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事情要拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.82,0:12:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能麻烦你跟我来一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.86,0:12:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.99,0:12:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.19,0:12:31.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没有放弃当厨师呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.13,0:12:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战以外的时间我要练习作菜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我需要AESTIVALIS的驾驶员啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.73,0:12:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找谁都好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.10,0:12:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像凉子啦，光，泉，甚至赤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.84,0:12:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.11,0:12:45.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非得是天河不可
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.67,0:12:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.54,0:12:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情就是这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.68,0:12:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好臭喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.95,0:12:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.58,0:12:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人都是这样子吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.72,0:12:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这房间真讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.99,0:12:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.25,0:13:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,控制室都被占据了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.06,0:13:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样危险的事又不能在舰桥做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.49,0:13:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…小心点 那里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.58,0:13:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我辛苦作的人型
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里可以做吗?除虫什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.40,0:13:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然外表不怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.84,0:13:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我已经跟思兼连线过不知几次了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.64,0:13:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,程式作得很好，看了也不会腻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.68,0:13:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.65,0:13:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.88,0:13:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AESTIVALIS?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.28,0:13:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,印象程式
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.38,0:13:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是可进入思兼的程式之内
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.41,0:13:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调查有问题的地方或修改
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.39,0:13:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓电脑空间的必杀扫除人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.98,0:13:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.86,0:13:38.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么，对我的兴趣有意见吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.68,0:13:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要跟我的主电脑连线然后操控摸拟器
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.30,0:13:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就会变成顶尖的电脑战士了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.37,0:13:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我来支援
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.30,0:13:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.94,0:13:50.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.82,0:13:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河AESTI启动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.50,0:13:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.74,0:14:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是在电脑里面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.86,0:14:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是被我影像化的电脑记忆中枢印象
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.93,0:14:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回想起来这是参照
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.63,0:14:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我失败七次的麻省理工学院图书馆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.27,0:14:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该往哪里走呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.63,0:14:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来带路
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.23,0:14:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.80,0:14:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边上去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.24,0:14:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右转，直走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.03,0:14:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的地是思兼的自主意识部份
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.37,0:14:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是正在覆盖中的新的军方程式
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.98,0:14:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那，干掉它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.62,0:14:38.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.15,0:14:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在攻击新程式的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.41,0:14:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,INSTALL会停止
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.03,0:14:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抚子会和以前一样继续反抗地球军
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.53,0:14:47.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.13,0:14:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先往前头
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.50,0:14:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去思兼的自主意识部份
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.17,0:14:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.77,0:14:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点不太忍心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.92,0:14:57.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好善良，天河
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.68,0:14:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.35,0:15:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.51,0:15:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思兼的自主意识部份
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.67,0:15:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的抚子身为抚子的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.87,0:15:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己确定自己存在的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.32,0:15:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己存在的证明?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.45,0:15:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的重要的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.93,0:15:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想忘也忘不了的重要的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.00,0:15:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记忆…回忆…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.22,0:15:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想忘记也忘不了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.13,0:15:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己就是自己的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.33,0:15:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他稍微忘掉一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.31,0:15:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他忘记?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.11,0:15:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.88,0:15:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个伸出来的部份
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.20,0:15:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请把那部份剪掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.48,0:15:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.95,0:15:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过枝芽还会再长出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.54,0:15:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一天思兼会记起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.18,0:15:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后抚子不会改变自己的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.89,0:15:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.12,0:15:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思兼，稍微忘却吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.40,0:15:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后长大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.31,0:16:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 你只要假装服从联合军的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.90,0:16:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抚子仍然还是抚子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.36,0:16:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.13,0:16:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.33,0:16:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了，明人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.53,0:16:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.50,0:16:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么出来了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.93,0:16:23.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电脑的异物排除意识
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.30,0:16:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是思兼的自卫反应
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.07,0:16:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是不想忘记重要记忆的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.04,0:16:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶，这是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.48,0:16:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.41,0:16:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激钢人3
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.15,0:16:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.25,0:16:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是思兼输入的资料中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.19,0:16:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最强，最正确的，正义的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.46,0:16:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他当成是自己的伙伴了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.26,0:16:54.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为思兼和你一起看过激钢人的录影带
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.46,0:16:58.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这样也用不着变成激钢人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.77,0:17:02.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为最了解激钢人的人是你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.17,0:17:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.64,0:17:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要我跟激钢人战斗吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.27,0:17:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.74,0:17:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊，明人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.84,0:17:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把激钢人什么的干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.61,0:17:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.71,0:17:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你，请战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.12,0:17:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.65,0:17:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方似乎不想放过你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.95,0:17:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激钢光束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.92,0:17:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.62,0:17:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激钢飞切
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.87,0:17:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行，打不过他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.50,0:17:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方是激钢人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.50,0:17:36.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会赢的，天河一定可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.91,0:17:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对那个机器人的思念应该比思兼更强
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.58,0:17:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…思念
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.85,0:17:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.88,0:17:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激钢人!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.36,0:17:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威力不相上下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.16,0:17:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激钢光束
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.50,0:18:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激钢飞踢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.67,0:18:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样分不出胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.34,0:18:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，由人来操纵我方比较不利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.28,0:18:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.38,0:18:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为人类的天河\N对那机器人从很久以前就非常了解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.72,0:18:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且一直喜爱着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.45,0:18:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人的思念是不可能轮的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.82,0:18:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的话真让我高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.96,0:18:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从很久以前，一直喜爱着...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.19,0:18:33.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.70,0:18:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.57,0:18:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激钢人从第十七集开始换成激钢人V
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.06,0:18:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.71,0:18:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦幻的变形模式!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.51,0:18:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙钢人你知道吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.42,0:19:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.87,0:19:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自卫反应消灭记忆修正完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.10,0:19:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河 剩的下只有尽快解决新程式
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.01,0:19:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去一切都会被消除的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.48,0:19:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.38,0:19:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是没问题吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.48,0:19:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被那些家伙发现的话就惨了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.57,0:19:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.35,0:19:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚刚就对调查团的电脑灌入假资料了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.55,0:19:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管放手干吧，明人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.52,0:19:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.45,0:19:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙钢人只有设定资料
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.48,0:19:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并没出现在电视上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.54,0:19:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也只有在凯的设定专辑里看过而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.27,0:19:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.24,0:19:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河的信念真的很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.31,0:20:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.72,0:20:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.79,0:20:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来，抚子的电脑，思兼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.63,0:20:09.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然还有抚子自身
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.69,0:20:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是表面没有发现任何异状
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.26,0:20:13.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺利顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.83,0:20:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球会赢的，这场战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.63,0:20:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吗?舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.17,0:20:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀，那当然
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.67,0:20:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.40,0:20:22.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.80,0:20:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微速前进，右满舵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.14,0:20:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微速前进，右满舵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.08,0:20:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"那忘不了的日子"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.10,0:20:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"现在为此而活着"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.79,0:20:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.20,0:20:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在寻找
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.30,0:20:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的感动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.05,0:21:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有纯粹的情感沉睡其中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.60,0:21:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要追寻梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.85,0:21:13.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑容与泪水的数目就会渐渐增多
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.60,0:21:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.53,0:21:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时想要更像自我地去感受风
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.11,0:21:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不属于其他人的我自己的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.05,0:21:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要去发掘
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.70,0:21:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充满速度感心跳加速的冒险
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.24,0:21:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当明人离开百合香的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.04,0:21:52.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虚构与现实的分界崩溃了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.24,0:21:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怖，厉害，呕心沥血的杰作终于诞生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.82,0:21:59.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充满精彩动作的绚烂豪华大作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.35,0:22:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,献给全国的好孩子及妈妈们的豪华贡献
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.69,0:22:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在职场，学校，家庭独占话题的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.99,0:22:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回，机动战舰抚子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.33,0:22:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"真实"不是只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.19,0:22:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起看哟
